== Surrounding Facilities, etc. == * {{ill|Tokyo Fire Department|ja|東京消防庁|12=draft}}{{ill|Ome Fire Station|ja|青梅消防署|12=draft}} Hinatawada Branch Office * Rinchuan Garden * {{ill|Meibakuin|ja|明白院|12=draft}}: One of the Tama-Ome {{ill|Seven Lucky Gods|ja|七福神|12=draft}}, enshrining {{ill|Fukurokuju|ja|福禄寿|12=draft}}<ref>[http://ome7.tokyo/meibakuin/ Meibakuin Tama-Ome Seven Lucky Gods Tour]. Tama-Ome Seven Lucky Gods Association</ref> * {{ill|Hinatawada Nursery School|ja|日向和田保育園|12=draft}}
